    <p>This Shipping Policy explains how Buddy9Nine delivers orders inside <strong>Langa</strong>. We aim to provide a fast, reliable, and safe delivery experience.</p>

    <section>
      <h2>Delivery Area</h2>
      <p>We currently deliver <strong>only within Langa</strong>. If your address is outside Langa, you will be notified during checkout and we will advise on alternative collection or delivery arrangements.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Delivery Time</h2>
      <p>Our target delivery time is <strong>60 minutes</strong> from the moment payment is confirmed. This applies to orders placed during our delivery hours and when items are in stock.</p>
      <div class="note">
        <strong>Note:</strong> Delivery time may increase due to heavy demand, severe weather, road closures, or other events outside our control. We will notify you by SMS or WhatsApp if a delay is expected.
      </div>
    </section>

