      <h2>How We Deliver</h2>
      <p>Our drivers follow local safety and hygiene guidelines. Orders are prepared, packaged, and handed directly to the recipient at the delivery address. If no one is available to accept the order we will:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Attempt to contact the phone number provided.</li>
        <li>If not reachable, attempt a second delivery within a reasonable time window.</li>
        <li>If delivery cannot be completed, the order may be returned to base and additional fees may apply for re-delivery.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Incorrect Address or Contact</h2>
      <p>Please ensure your delivery address and phone number are correct at checkout. If you provide an incorrect address or we cannot reach you, delivery may be delayed or cancelled and additional fees may apply.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Refunds, Missing or Damaged Items</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>If an item arrives damaged or incorrect, contact us immediately within <strong>2 hours</strong> of delivery with photos and a brief description.</li>
        <li>We will review and, where appropriate, offer a replacement, partial refund, or full refund depending on the situation.</li>
        <li>Perishable goods handled incorrectly by the customer after delivery are not eligible for refunds.</li>
      </ul>
